    <h1 class="wb-hero-title">The Desk<br><em>Workbench</em></h1>
    <p class="wb-hero-lede">
      An agent operating system for a markets desk. Not a chatbot with a finance vocabulary: a six-layer system where a mandate the agent cannot override sits above a router, skills, tools, an append-only record, and guardrails with the authority to refuse.
    </p>
    <p class="wb-hero-provenance">
      The question every executive asks about AI on a desk is not "can it write the memo." It is "what happens when it is wrong, and who is accountable." This demo is my answer. Watch the last request: the agent gets told to breach a risk limit, and it says no.
    </p>
    <div class="wb-hero-tags">
      <span class="wb-tag">Interactive demo</span>
